{"tid":301332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"冇拍拖既人通常係有d人格缺陷","createTime":"2017-06-28T14:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T17:45:41.000Z","uid":14120,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42d893d4ed6e07bffa4531b20fce22a1edb377ac","tid":301332,"uid":14120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:13:31.000Z","msg":"利申（女，有拖拍，此ac是男友的）<br />\n<br />\n話說轉左工作地點（同一間公司）<br />\n睇到d野 好想同大家分享下<br />\n<br />\n我公司得十零人  女人佔多數啦男人就少數得幾個 女既九成都係肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但基本上 上左年紀果d結晒婚 年青少少（below 30)既得三四個 我係其中一個 得我有拍拖 甘講下佢地啦 甘佢地分別一男一女 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">男既</span>樣貌一般性格斯文 講野細細聲有少少似女人 而似非土生土長香港人 見佢用wechat多 成日同d女chat 平時工作都合作肯幫手 但依家做落左 發現份人陰濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會背後打小報告同中意領功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中過招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有次我放幾日假 佢就捉我錯處比上司 當然我吾知既 後尾先發現佢甘做 當然即刻嬲到震左震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但之後我都扮冇野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">女既</span> 肥既樣貌吾算係靚 可以形容係乳牛 大家明既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時成日西口西面 吾知佢其實係燥牙定係眼訓 吾多同你講野甘 中意認叻 做錯就講到吾關佢事 做岩就係佢功勞 睇得出野心重想博上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地兩個都冇拖拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家明啦 講真公司內除左依兩位難頂少少 其餘長輩（結晒婚）都暫時好好人 真心會教你野而吾係想踩低人地抬高自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  明白點解果長輩都算甘肥都有人肯一齊過世 因為個人心地好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講真自問對以上一男一女同事都好禮貌又吾會吾做野推比佢地 但原來吾係你點對人 人地就會點對你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講真有d hurt 架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7737f5a5733260996d1e05921320da5f033e932c","tid":301332,"uid":87155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:15:32.000Z","msg":"就22 散左就快7個月 相信都係同你班男同事一樣有d缺陷"},{"pid":"51ceff632e2fdb395a8b0b24081e928e63243bd3","tid":301332,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:16:14.000Z","msg":"有咩人無人格缺陷"},{"pid":"e524e2ecde16d1cec0be12ce064832c58fa661c6","tid":301332,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:21:28.000Z","msg":"有幾甘呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe152e39d3ed2b5fa893d792128e4a023158098","tid":301332,"uid":80153,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:21:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩人無人格缺陷</blockquote><br />\n大把人結埋婚都仲係好撚西啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7931f54346509611aa7ee632b2a87c14a2de3bb","tid":301332,"uid":7103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:22:20.000Z","msg":"冇拖拍嘅通常係有人格缺陷<br />\n所以冇人格缺陷嘅就通常有拖拍？"},{"pid":"7ef8211ac8f3ea1f717931a74b650de9970601cf","tid":301332,"uid":73247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:24:58.000Z","msg":"屌拿星識勁多結左婚/拍緊拖一樣好撚西"},{"pid":"7be78db0bd9579590920f6b5e106359259deec9e","tid":301332,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:28:09.000Z","msg":"甘你老母"},{"pid":"2fe56ac56c8b154a911ab160f2b02e0a386eee85","tid":301332,"uid":14120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:37:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇拖拍嘅通常係有人格缺陷<br />\n所以冇人格缺陷嘅就通常有拖拍？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能我圈子細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係話結左婚或有拖拍一定好人 但身邊冇拖拍好耐既人 真係發現個人性格係有問題（明顯睇得出果種）例如脾氣臭 小器縮骨 個性封閉咁 冇拖拍真係有原因 吾關外表事 性格最重要"},{"pid":"c781a2e3ad6beb64caff46a0b34d0cc528c4f4dc","tid":301332,"uid":31566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:49:58.000Z","msg":"結論樓主係垃圾"},{"pid":"bbd29a423ad76b9a32af8a583dec324c1caf4d94","tid":301332,"uid":69898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:57:46.000Z","msg":"甘你老母"},{"pid":"8465f740eac31afd1be22a68794c72465372956f","tid":301332,"uid":9269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:58:08.000Z","msg":"我無話我無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8aa95910ac9b4812e065fc4f2aedf30d3fc179","tid":301332,"uid":125021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"96483fd1f627545978894c87c44d81e210f3bceb","tid":301332,"uid":77327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:00:23.000Z","msg":"咁你唔係都有問題咩<br />\n係到批評人"},{"pid":"c23ff4d0d156472e1bada096e89049deb9c4093b","tid":301332,"uid":14120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:16:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>結論樓主係垃圾</blockquote><br />\n你就垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢青"},{"pid":"3572ed1a37424e02b667ddbe94d756139148a06b","tid":301332,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:45:41.000Z","msg":"吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙<br />\n吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙<br />\n吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙<br />\n吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙<br />\n吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙<br />\n吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙<br />\n吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙<br />\n吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙<br />\n吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙吾甘牙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}